{
  "Logarithmic Differentiation": "对对数区分",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "What is d/dx[x^x] using logarithmic differentiation?": "d/dx[xxx] 使用对数区分是什么?",
  "Let y = x^x. ln(y) = x*ln(x). Differentiate: y'/y = ln(x) + 1. So y' = x^x(ln(x) + 1).": "Let y = xx. x. in(y) = x*ln(x). difficate: y'/y = In(x) + 1. 所以 y' = xx(x) + 1.",
  "Using logarithmic differentiation, what is d/dx[(x+1)^3 * (x+2)^4]?": "使用对数区分, d/dx[(x+1)3 * (x+2)4] 是什么?",
  "Let y = (x+1)^3(x+2)^4. ln(y) = 3ln(x+1) + 4ln(x+2). y'/y = 3/(x+1) + 4/(x+2). So y' = (x+1)^3(x+2)^4[3/(x+1) + 4/(x+2)]. Note: the last option is also correct via the product rule.": "Let y = (x+1)%3(x+2)%4. In(y) = 3ln(x+1) + 4ln(x+2) + 4ln(x+2) y'y = 3/(x+1) + 4/(x+2), 所以y' = (x+1)3(x+2)4[3(x+1) + 4/(x+2)。 注意: 最后一个选项通过产品规则也是正确的 。",
  "What is d/dx[x^(sin(x))]?": "d/dx[x}(sin(x)]是什么?",
  "Let y = x^(sin(x)). ln(y) = sin(x)*ln(x). y'/y = cos(x)*ln(x) + sin(x)/x. So y' = x^(sin(x))[cos(x)*ln(x) + sin(x)/x].": "Let y = x(sin(x). In(y) = sin(x) *ln(x).y'y = cos(x) *ln(x.x) + sin(x)/x. soy' = x}(sin(x)) [cos(x) *ln(x) + sin(x)/x]。",
  "What is d/dx[(2x)^(3x)] using logarithmic differentiation?": "d/dx[( 2x) ( 3x)] 使用对数区分是什么?",
  "Let y = (2x)^(3x). ln(y) = 3x*ln(2x). y'/y = 3*ln(2x) + 3x*(1/x) = 3*ln(2x) + 3 = 3[ln(2x)+1]. So y' = (2x)^(3x)*3[ln(2x)+1].": "Let y = (2x) = (3x). in(y) = 3x * ln(2x).y = 3* ln(2x) + 3x* (1/x) = 3* ln(2x) + 3 = 3[(2x)+1]. y' = 2x) = (3x) * 3 [(2x)+1] 。",
  "What is d/dx[x^(1/x)] using logarithmic differentiation?": "d/dx[x(1/x)]使用对数区别是什么?",
  "Let y = x^(1/x). ln(y) = ln(x)/x. y'/y = (1/x * x - ln(x))/x^2 = (1 - ln(x))/x^2. So y' = x^(1/x)(1-ln(x))/x^2.": "y=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx2=1xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "Using logarithmic differentiation, what is d/dx[(x^2+1)^5 / (x^3-1)^2]?": "使用对数区别, d/dx[(x__2+1)+1]5 /(x__3-1)2)是什么?",
  "ln(y) = 5ln(x^2+1) - 2ln(x^3-1). y'/y = 5*2x/(x^2+1) - 2*3x^2/(x^3-1) = 10x/(x^2+1) - 6x^2/(x^3-1). y' = y * [10x/(x^2+1) - 6x^2/(x^3-1)].": "In(y) = 5ln(x__2+1) - 2ln(x__3-1). y'y = 5*2x/(x__2+1) - 2*3x%2(x__3-1) = 10x/(x__2+1) - 6x%2(x__3-1). y' = y * [10x/(x__2+1) - 6x%2/(x__3-1)]]",
  "What is d/dx[(cos(x))^x]?": "d/dx[(cos(x)x)x]是什么?",
  "Let y = (cos(x))^x. ln(y) = x*ln(cos(x)). y'/y = ln(cos(x)) + x*(-sin(x)/cos(x)) = ln(cos(x)) - x*tan(x). So y' = (cos(x))^x[ln(cos(x)) - x*tan(x)].": "Let y = (cos(x)x.)x. In(y) = x*ln(cos(x)x)y'/y = In(cos(x)x) + x*(sin(x)/cos(x)x) = In(cos(x)x) - x*tan(x)x. y' = (cos(x)x)xx[ln(cos(x)x) - x*tan(x)]。",
  "What is d/dx[x^(e^x)]?": "d/dx[x}(e_x)]是什么?",
  "Let y = x^(e^x). ln(y) = e^x*ln(x). y'/y = e^x*ln(x) + e^x*(1/x) = e^x(ln(x) + 1/x). So y' = x^(e^x)*e^x(ln(x) + 1/x).": "Let y = x(ex). in(y) = ex *ln(x).y = ex*ln(x) + ex* (1/x) = ex(x) + 1/x. y' = x(ex) * ex(x) + 1/x. 所以y' = x(ex) * ex(x) + 1/x.",
  "If y = (x^2 + 1)^(x^2), what is y'(0)?": "如果y = (x% 2 + 1) = (x% 2) = (x% 2 + 1) = (x% 2), 什么是 y' (0) ?",
  "ln(y) = x^2*ln(x^2+1). y'/y = 2x*ln(x^2+1) + x^2*2x/(x^2+1). At x = 0: y = 1^0 = 1, y'/1 = 0 + 0 = 0. So y'(0) = 0.": "In(y) = x% 2 * ln( x% 2+1) y'y = 2x *ln( x% 2+1) + x% 2* 2x/ (x% 2+1) 。在x = 0: y= 1 y= 1, y'/1 = 0 + 0 = 0。 y' (0) = 0 。",
  "What is 'logarithmic differentiation'?": "什么是“对数差异”?",
  "Logarithmic differentiation involves: (1) taking ln of both sides: ln(y) = ln(f(x)), (2) using log properties to simplify, (3) differentiating both sides, and (4) solving for y'. It is especially useful for functions of the form f(x)^g(x).": "对数区分涉及:(1) 在两边使用: In(y) = In(f(x)),(2) 使用日志属性简化,(3) 区分两边,(4) 解决y'。 它对于表f(x) g(x) 的功能特别有用。",
  "A population model uses P(t) = t^t for a certain rapidly-growing organism over a short period. What is P'(2)?": "人口模型在短时期内对某一快速增长的有机体使用P(t) = tt。 P'(2)是什么?",
  "P'(t) = t^t(ln(t) + 1). At t = 2: P'(2) = 2^2(ln(2) + 1) = 4(ln(2) + 1) (approximately 6.77).": "P'(t) = tt(ln(t) + 1). t = 2: P'(2) = 22(ln(2) + 1) = 4(ln(2) + 1) (约合6.77)。",
  "A chemical reaction rate is R = k * [A]^2 * [B]^3, where [A] and [B] are concentrations. Using logarithmic differentiation, what is dR/dt in terms of R, d[A]/dt, and d[B]/dt?": "化学反应率是R = k * [A]%2 * [B]%3,其中[A]和[B]为浓度。使用对数区分,R、d[A]/dt和d[B]/dt的 dR/dt是什么?",
  "ln(R) = ln(k) + 2ln[A] + 3ln[B]. Differentiate: (1/R)*dR/dt = 2*(1/[A])*d[A]/dt + 3*(1/[B])*d[B]/dt. So dR/dt = R[2/A * dA/dt + 3/B * dB/dt].": "In(R) = In(k) + 2ln[A] + 3ln[B]。区别:(1/R) * dR/dt = 2*(1/[A] * d[A]/dt + 3*(1/[B] * d[B]]/dt. So dR/dt = R[2/A * dA/dt + 3/B * dB/dt]。",
  "An economist models utility as U = x^(0.4) * y^(0.6), where x and y are quantities of two goods. If x = 10, y = 20, dx/dt = 2, dy/dt = -1, what is dU/dt?": "经济学家模型效用为 U = x(0. 4) * y(0. 6), x 和 y 是两种货物的数量。如果 x = 10, y = 20, dx/ dt = 2, dy/ dt = -1, 什么是 dU/ dt ?",
  "ln(U) = 0.4*ln(x) + 0.6*ln(y). dU/dt = U[0.4/x * dx/dt + 0.6/y * dy/dt] = U[0.4(2)/10 + 0.6(-1)/20] = U[0.08 - 0.03] = 0.05U.": "In(U) = 0.4*ln(x) + 0.6*ln(y).dU/dt = U[0.4/x * dx/dt + 0.6/y * dy/dt] = U[0.4(2)/10 + 0.6(-1)/20] = U[0.08 - 0.03 = 0.05U。",
  "A physics model uses f(x) = (sin(x))^(cos(x)) for a specialized wave. What is f'(pi/2)?": "物理模型使用 f(x) = (sin(x)) = (cos(x) ) 来进行特殊波。 f' (pi/2) 是什么?",
  "At x = pi/2: sin(pi/2) = 1, cos(pi/2) = 0. f(pi/2) = 1^0 = 1. ln(f) = cos(x)*ln(sin(x)). f'/f = -sin(x)*ln(sin(x)) + cos(x)*cos(x)/sin(x). At pi/2: f'/1 = -1*ln(1) + 0 = 0. So f'(pi/2) = 0.": "At x = pi/2: sin (pi/2) = 1, cos(pi/2) = 0. f(pi) = 1, f(f) = 1, In(x) = cos(x) * ln(sin(x) f'/f) = -sin(x) * ln(sin(x) * ln(sin(x) ) + cos(x) * (x) /sin(x)。 At pi/2: f'/1 = -1* l(1) + 0 = 0。so f' (pi) = 0。",
  "A company's revenue is R = p^n * q^m where p = price, q = quantity, n = 1.5, m = 0.8. If price increases at 5%/year and quantity at 3%/year, what is the percentage rate of change of revenue?": "公司的收入是R=pn * qm,p=价格,q=数量,n=1.5,m=0.8。如果年价格上涨5%,年价格上涨3%,收入变化的百分比率是多少?",
  "ln(R) = 1.5*ln(p) + 0.8*ln(q). (1/R)*dR/dt = 1.5*(1/p)*dp/dt + 0.8*(1/q)*dq/dt = 1.5(0.05) + 0.8(0.03) = 0.075 + 0.024 = 0.099 = 9.9%.": "In(R)=1.5*ln(p)+0.8*ln(q) (1/R)*dR/dt=1.5*(1/p)*dp/dt+0.8*(1/q)*dq/dt=1.5(0.05)+0.8(0.03)=0.075+0.024=0.099=9.9%。",
  "A biologist studies growth with G(t) = t^(sqrt(t)) for a certain cell culture. What is G'(4)?": "G(t) = t(sqrt(t)) 的生物学研究为某种细胞文化而增长。 G'(4)是什么?",
  "ln(G) = sqrt(t)*ln(t). G'/G = (1/(2sqrt(t)))*ln(t) + sqrt(t)/t = ln(t)/(2sqrt(t)) + 1/sqrt(t). At t = 4: G = 4^2 = 16. G'/16 = ln(4)/4 + 1/2. Actually G'/16 = ln(4)/(2*2) + 2/4 = ln(4)/4 + 1/2. Hmm, let me recheck: 1/sqrt(4) = 1/2. So G'/16 = ln(4)/4 + 1/2.": "In(G) = sqrt(t) *ln(t) = sqrt(t) *ln(t) + sqrt(t) /t = In(t) /(sqrt(t) ) + 1/sqrt(t) 。在 t = 4: G= 4= 42 = 16. G'/16 = In(4)/4 + 1/2。实际上,G'16 = In(4)/(4) = In(4)/(2*2) + 2/4 = In(4)/4 + + 1/2。嗯,让我重新检查: 1/sqrt(4) = 1/2。G'16 = In(4)/4+ 1/2。",
  "An investment banker models compound returns as V(t) = (1 + r(t))^t, where r(t) = 0.05 + 0.01*sin(t). What is the logarithmic derivative (1/V * dV/dt) at t = 0?": "投资银行家模型复合回报值为 V(t) = 1 + r(t) = 0.05 + 0.01 *sin(t) r(t) = 0.05 + 0.01 *sin(t) 。 t = 0 的对数衍生物(1/V * dV/dt)是什么?",
  "ln(V) = t*ln(1+r(t)). d/dt[ln(V)] = ln(1+r) + t*r'/(1+r). At t = 0: r = 0.05, r' = 0.01*cos(0) = 0.01. So d/dt[ln(V)] = ln(1.05) + 0*0.01/1.05 = ln(1.05). Wait -- at t = 0, the second term is 0. So the answer is just ln(1.05). Actually with t=0: ln(1.05) + 0 = ln(1.05).": "In(V) = t *ln(1+r(t) d/dt[ln(V)] = In(1+r) + t*r'/(1+r). t= 0: r= 0.05, r' = 0.01 *cos(0) = 0.01。 所以d/dt[ln(V) = IN(1.05) + 0* 0.01/1.05 = In(1.05)。 等等,在t = 0,第二个术语是 0。所以答案是 IN(1.05) 。实际上, t= 0: In(1.05) + 0 = IN(1.05)。",
  "A pharmacologist models drug potency as P = (C/C_0)^n * e^(-kt), where C = concentration, C_0 = reference, n = 2. Using logarithmic differentiation, what is (1/P)*dP/dt?": "P=(C/C_0)n * e(-kt),C=浓度,C_0=参考,n=2. 使用对数区分法,什么是(1/P)*dP/dt?",
  "ln(P) = 2*ln(C/C_0) - kt = 2*ln(C) - 2*ln(C_0) - kt. (1/P)*dP/dt = 2*(1/C)*dC/dt - k.": "In(P) = 2 *ln(C/C_0) - kt = 2 *ln(C) - 2 *ln(C_0) - kt. (1/P) *dP/dt = 2*(1/C) *dC/dt - k。",
  "A thermal model uses T(x) = x^(ln(x)). What is T'(e)?": "热模型使用T(x) = x(ln(x) 。 T'(e)是什么?",
  "ln(T) = (ln(x))^2. T'/T = 2*ln(x)/x. At x = e: T = e^1 = e, T'/e = 2*1/e = 2/e. So T'(e) = e * 2/e = 2.": "In(T) = (ln(xx)) = 2. T'/T = 2 *ln(x)/x。在x = e: T = e = e = e = 1 e, T'/e = 2 *1/e = 2/e. 所以 T'(e) = e * 2/e = 2。",
  "A materials scientist uses the stress-strain formula sigma = A * epsilon^n, where A = 500 MPa, n = 0.3, and epsilon (strain) is increasing at 0.001/s. What is the rate of change of stress when epsilon = 0.1?": "材料科学家使用压力-压力-压力-压力公式 sigma = A * epsilonn, 其中A= 500 MPa, n = 0.3, 和 epsilon (压力-压力-压力-压力-压力-压力-压力公式 sigma = A * epsilonn)在0.001/s 增长。 当 Essilon = 0.1 时,压力变化速率是多少?",
  "d(sigma)/dt = A * n * epsilon^(n-1) * d(epsilon)/dt = 500 * 0.3 * (0.1)^(-0.7) * 0.001. This equals 0.15 * (0.1)^(-0.7) MPa/s (approximately 0.15 * 5.01 = 0.75 MPa/s).": "d(sigma)/dt = A * n * epsilon}(n-1) * d(epsilon)/dt = 500 * 0.3 * (0.1) {(-07) * 0.001。这等于 0.15 * (0.1) {(0.7) MPa/s (约0.15 * 5.01 = 0.75 MPa/s)。",
  "What does 'percentage rate of change' mean?": "“百分比变化率”意味着什么?",
  "The percentage rate of change is 100 * f'(x)/f(x). It expresses the relative rate as a percentage. For exponential growth y = Ce^(kt), the percentage rate is 100k%.": "百分比变化率为100 * f'(x)/f(x). 表示相对比率为百分比。对于指数增长 y = Ce(kt),百分比为100k%。"
}